 satellite and ict and other international services the companys other business segment sells electronic products and properties chunghwa telecom co ltd was founded in  and is based in taipei taiwancorporate governancechunghwa telecom co ltd’s iss governance qualityscore as of na is na the pillar scores are audit na board na shareholder rights na compensation nacorporate governance scores courtesy of institutional shareholder services iss scores indicate decile rank relative to index or region a decile score of  indicates lower governance risk while a  indicates higher governance riskyahoo small businessdata disclaimerhelpsuggestionsprivacyabout our adsterms updated chunghwa telecom co ltd cht company profile  reuterscom x edition united states africa américa latina عربي argentina brasil canada  deutschland españa france india italia  méxico россия united kingdom united states profile chunghwa telecom co ltd cht related topics stocksstock screenertelecommunications servicesintegrated telecommunications services overview news key developments people charts financials analysts research pulse cht on new york consolidated usd  jul  change  chg   prev close  open  days high  days low  volume  avg vol  wk high  wk low  full description chunghwa telecom co ltd incorporated on june   is a telecommunications service provider in taiwan the companys segments include domestic fixed communications business mobile communications business internet business international fixed communications business and others the company also focuses on selected information and communication technology ict services and advanced developments in addition to developing ict businesses it also pursues ict projects from both public and private sectorsdomestic fixed communications businessthe domestic fixed communications business segment is engaged in the provision of local telephone services domestic long distance telephone services broadband access and related services the companys domestic fixed communications business includes local and domestic long distance leased line services wireless fidelity wifi services multimedia on demand services and other domestic services including ict corporate solution services cloud computing services and bill handling services the company also provides leased lines to other mobile and fixedline service operators for interconnection with its fixedline network and for connection within their networks the company offers valueadded services vas services including call waiting caller identification call forwarding threeparty calls ring back tone and voicemailthe company provides intelligent network services over its domestic long distance network including tollfree calling and virtual private networks vpn services and others the company provides broadband internet access through connections based on its fiber to the x fttx and asymmetric digital subscriber line adsl technologies its fttx service offers downlink speeds of over six     and  megabits per second mbps matched with uplink speeds of approximately two five     and  mbps respectively its adsl service offers downlink speeds that range from  mbps to  mbps and uplink speeds that range from  kilobits per second kbps to  kbpsthe company provides domestic leased line services in taiwan leased line services involve offering exclusive lines that allow pointtopoint connection for voice and data traffic leased lines are used by business customers to assemble their own private networks and by telecommunications service providers to establish networks to offer telecommunications services it provides data transmission services to corporate customers in taiwan it also provides leased lines to other mobile and fixedline service operators for interconnection with its fixedline network and for connection within their networksthe company has a total of approximately  million residential and business customers that leased its access points in addition it has established over  hot spots in public areas such as convenience stores airports and international convention centers where its smartphone subscribers can access their wifi network and help to offload mobile data network traffic using video streaming technology through a settop box that connects to its fttx and adsl data connections its multimedia on demand mod customers can access television programs videoondemand and other services it has over  broadcasting channels and over  hours of ondemand programs and serves approximately  million customers it offers over  high definition hd channels and other hd videoondemand programming such as sports movies and knowledge materialsmobile communications businessthe company offers mobile services in taiwan the mobile communications business segment is engaged in the provision of mobile services sales of mobile handsets and data cards and related services its third generation roaming contracts include over  networks in approximately  countries as well as its secondgeneration global system for mobile communications gsm roaming contracts include over  networks in approximately  countries and its g general packetswitched radio services gprs roaming contracts include over  networks in approximately  countriesthe company offers an international roaming network it has also established fourth generation long term evaluation lte roaming contracts with over  networks in approximately  countries the company offers prepaid card and prepaid third generation card services the company has approximately  million prepaid customers it is involved in the distribution and sales of mobile handsets tablets and data cards for use on its mobile network to customers through its directly owned stores its subsidiary senao international co ltd and also through thirdparty retailers its other mobile services include ict services corporate solution and bill handling servicesinternet businessthe internet business segment is engaged in the provision of hinet services and related services the companys internet business includes its internet service provider internet vas data communication services internet data center idc services and ict and other internet services hinet has approximately  million subscribers the companys hinet portal at wwwhinetnet provides vas to its customers such as network security blog travel games elearning financial information music video antivirus and links to other portals its internet video portal at wwwhichannelhinetnet offers online entertainment services through the internet in particular its hinet broadband fttx and adsl subscribers can access music television programs movies and other multimedia content on demandthe company provides a range of managed data services including frame relay services asynchronous transfer mode services and vpn services frame relay services provide data communications linking remote sites asynchronous transfer mode services are used to handle highbandwidth integrated voice video data and internet traffic between sites idcs are facilities providing the physical environment necessary to keep computer network servers running at all times these facilities are customdesigned with air conditioning temperature control systems secure access reliable electricity supply and connections to highbandwidth internet networks data centers house protect and maintain network server computers that store and deliver internet and other network content such as website pages applications and data it offers colocation website hosting and application service provider servicesinternational fixed communications businessthe companys international fixed communications business includes international long distance telephone services international leased line services international data services satellite services and ict and other international services the company provides international long distance telephone services in taiwan it provides wholesale international long distance services to international simple resale operators that do not possess their own telephone network or infrastructure its international long distance services consist primarily of international direct dial services and the wholesale of international long distance traffic it also provides data transmission services to corporate customers in taiwan its international data services include international internet protocol virtual private network ip vpn services and taiwan internet gateway services it has over two satellite communication centers that enable it to provide television broadcast satellite vas and backup systems for use in emergencies it also provides satellite services to southeast asiaothersthe others segment is engaged in the provision of nontelecom services and the corporate related items the other business segment includes its nontelecom services including property sales made by its subsidiary light era development co ltd and electronic products sales made by its subsidiary chunghwa precision test tech co ltd its ict service includes integrated services such as intelligent energy network ien intelligent transportation system its and internet of vehicles its ien service helps companies and corporations implement energy saving measures through computer analysis of data its its service provides navigation realtime traffic information and infotainment through mobile devices for cars and drivers the company offers internet of vehicles services including global positioning system gps audio and video streaming and car informationthe company competes with twm broadband new century infocomm tech co ltd asia pacific telecom taiwan optical platform co ltd kbro co ltd china network systems co ltd taiwan broadband communication co ltd taiwan optical platform co ltd taiwan intelligent fiber optic network taiwan mobile co ltd far eastone telecommunications co ltd taiwan star telecom corporation ltd seednet line and skype » full overview of cht company address chunghwa telecom co ltd  section hsinyi roadjhongjhen